@startuml sequence_diagram
title 선잇기 퍼즐 — 드래그 한 프레임 처리 시퀀스

actor 사용자
participant "Canvas" as C
participant "InputHandler" as I
participant "GameScene" as G
participant "Board" as B
participant "PathBuilder" as P
participant "SpatialHash" as H
participant "Sound" as S

== pointer down (dot 위) ==
사용자 -> C : pointerdown(x, y)
C -> I : pointerdown event
I -> G : onDown(cssX, cssY)
G -> S : ensureCtx()  (autoplay 우회)
G -> G : screenToWorld → world(x, y)
G -> B : findDotAt(world)
B --> G : Dot
G -> B : startPath(dot.id)
B -> H : (기존 같은색 path 제거)
B -> P : new PathBuilder(...)
G -> S : playStart()

== pointer move (드래그) ==
사용자 -> C : pointermove(x, y)
C -> I : pointermove event
I -> G : onMove(cssX, cssY)
G -> B : updatePath(world)
B -> P : onPointerMove(p)

note over P
파이프라인:
1) tryRewind() — 과거 세그먼트 근처면 pop 체이닝
2) MIN_STEP 검사
3) firstDotHit — foreign dot 통과 차단 / 같은 색이면 finalize
4) crossesOtherPath — hash.query → 교차 검사
5) crossesSelf — 직전 세그먼트 제외
6) pushSegment + hash.insert
end note

P -> H : query(newSeg)
H --> P : 후보들
P -> P : 검사 통과 → push
P -> H : insert(pathId, newSeg)
P --> B : MoveResult { kind: extended }
B --> G : MoveResult

alt 같은 색 dot 도달
  P --> B : MoveResult { kind: finalized, endDot }
  B -> B : finalized.set(colorId, ...)
  G -> S : playFinalize()
  G -> B : isCleared() ?
  B --> G : true / false
  alt 클리어
    G -> S : playClear()
    G -> G : effects.clearBurst()
    G -> G : onClear() callback
  end
end

== pointer up ==
사용자 -> C : pointerup
C -> I : pointerup event
I -> G : onUp()
G -> B : endPath()  (finalize 안된 path는 cancel)

== 매 프레임 ==
G -> G : RAF loop
G -> G : effects.update(dt)
G -> "Renderer" : draw(board)
G -> "Renderer" : effects.draw(ctx)

@enduml
